I want them to encounter that.

65
00:03:42,713 --> 00:03:46,115
As for building their own intuition and building their own playtesting skills,

66
00:03:46,395 --> 00:03:50,319
we do that through practical exercises where they analyze the balance of an existing game

67
00:03:50,619 --> 00:03:52,060
or do balance on a game of their own.

68
